{help, syntax=--help, title=WorldWeaver Help
    [@topic
WorldWeaver is a text based game engine. If you are new to Interactive Fiction
(IF) you can get started by using --help getting started.
\n
Basic WorldWeaver Commands:
\n
credits
 - When playing a game, this will display the game's credits.
\n
quit
 - When playing a game, this will quit the current game and display the
   WorldWeaver home screen.
\n
exit
 - Exits WorldWeaver
    ]
}
